1613
01:27:31,604 --> 01:27:33,560
Rym: And it's usually an informed decision.

1614
01:27:33,720 --> 01:27:45,139
Rym: It is the decision of, while I could stay, I'm going to sacrifice the last hour, or last half hour, or last whatever, of this event in order to sleep so that I can do more the next day.

1615
01:27:45,260 --> 01:27:47,480
Rym: Like, it was always a decision, and I could've stayed.

1616
01:27:48,480 --> 01:27:49,061
