1625
01:28:24,860 --> 01:28:28,519
Scott: I just stayed, but Rym wanted to leave, and then I just sort of acquiesced.

1626
01:28:28,860 --> 01:28:35,286
Rym: Yes, basically, it's not like Scott was the trooper saying, "Man, Rym, fuck you, but we should

1627
01:28:35,327 --> 01:28:35,513
