1637
01:29:16,142 --> 01:29:18,260
Rym: Yes, there are no chairs except in the very back.

1638
01:29:18,480 --> 01:29:18,880
Scott: Exactly.

1639
01:29:19,100 --> 01:29:29,079
Scott: General admission just means it's the floor in front of the stage, and you walk out there, and you can just walk around except where there's people already standing, and then you can't walk there because of the laws of physics.

1640
01:29:30,440 --> 01:29:32,340
Scott: Seating means seats, right?

1641
01:29:32,480 --> 01:29:37,029
Scott: Well, at Otakon and such, the concerts have seats right up to the front, and it's sort of black.

1642
01:29:37,049 --> 01:29:37,740
