1644
01:29:43,800 --> 01:29:46,540
Scott: General admission is what concerts are about.

1645
01:29:46,700 --> 01:29:50,760
Scott: If your concert doesn't have general admission, that ruins even the best band in the world.

1646
01:29:51,061 --> 01:29:52,019
Scott: It kind of sucks.

1647
